Package com.coremedia.iso.boxes.rtp

Class Summary
HintInformationBox Contains SDP information to be used by a streaming server.
HintPacketsSentBox Represents two specifc hint statistic boxes.
HintStatisticBoxes Actual statistics about the hint track.
HintStatisticsBox Parent box for various hint statistics.
LargestHintPacketBox The largest packet, in bytes; includes 12-byte RTP header.
LargestHintPacketDurationBox The largest packet, in bytes; includes 12-byte RTP header.
LargestRelativeTransmissionTimeBox The largest relative transmission time, in milliseconds.
MaximumDataRateBox The maximum data rate.
PayloadTypeBox The largest packet, in bytes; includes 12-byte RTP header.
RtpHintSampleEntry Contains basic information about the (rtp-) hint samples in this track.
RtpMovieHintInformationBox  
RtpTrackSdpHintInformationBox Contains the information that will be used by the streaming server to create the SDP file.
SmallestRelativeTransmissionTimeBox The smallest relative transmission time, in milliseconds.
TimeScaleEntry The TimeScaleEntry is a required box in the additionalData array of a HintSampleEntry if the HintSampleEntry's type is 'rtp '.
